; Regression test for issue #739: prices/pricedb only show pricedb info for commodities listed in transactions (BZ#739)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/739
;
; BUG: GOOG has a P price entry but does not appear in any transaction.
; The `prices` and `pricedb` commands should show all commodities with
; price entries, but currently only show commodities that appear in transactions.
; Expected: both AAPL and GOOG appear. Actual: only AAPL appears.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/01 GOOG $100.00

2024/01/01 Buy stock
    Assets:Investments     10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test prices
2024/01/01 AAPL          $150.00
end test

test pricedb
P 2024/01/01 00:00:00 AAPL $150.00
end test
